2 Tuners + 1 non-Tuner "Vylon" monsterWhen this card is Synchro Summoned: Destroy all face-up monsters that were Normal Summoned/Set. Once per turn: You can target 1 "Vylon" monster in your Graveyard; equip that target to this card. During either player's turn, when a monster effect activates: You can send 1 Equip Card equipped to this card to the Graveyard; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that monster.
